<p><strong>SCP-CN-395：</strong>血肉聚合者<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3354275&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608084428" alt="OlivaFute" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3354275)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;">OlivaFute</a></span></p>
